Class SemanticHighlightings

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptolemy.backtrack.eclipse.plugin.editor.SemanticHighlightings

  • public class SemanticHighlightings
extends java.lang.Object
    Definition of a set of semantic highlightings. Each semantic highlighting is a subclass of SemanticHighlighting and handles a special type of semantic elements.
